Paper: hep-th/9609173

Date: 1996-09-21

Title: Particle-Particle-String Vertex

Authors: Nobuyuki Ishibashi (KEK)

Comments: 9 pages, LaTex file

We study a theory of particles interacting with strings. Considering such atheory for Type IIA superstring will give some clue about M-theory. As a firststep toward such a theory, we construct the particle-particle-stringinteraction vertex generalizing the D-particle boundary state.